    ScarabHardware miniSpartan6+ SoC based on Migen/MiSoC

[> Getting started
1. Install Python3 and your vendor's software

2. Obtain LiteX and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litex --recursive
  cd litex
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

3. Obtain LiteDRAM and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litedram
  cd litedarm
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

6. Build the gateware and software:
  make minispartan6_base
  make load

[> Status:
BaseSoC with 16 bits SDR @ 80Mbps/pin.

